#Steps Taken

Created a Kinesis Data Stream
Injected mock data into the Kinesis stream
Verified data availability in the Kinesis stream
Configured a Lambda function to fetch and store Kinesis data in DynamoDB, triggered by the Kinesis stream
Tested and validated Lambda function code
Setup DynamoDB instance
Conducted system tests by sending 100 records to the Kinesis stream
Executed a DynamoDB scan operation to retrieve stored data
